ana_Steam.jpg?t=1701997947\" /><br><br>MidKnight Story's adventure begins when Paran discovers the sword called <strong>Durindana</strong>. The legendary sword will serve him in more than just combat against enemies, in fact it will be the very key he needs to unlock the world of MidKnight Story and to reach new levels within it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084830/extras/SwordShowcase_Steam.gif?t=1701997947\" /><br><br>The sword will be upgradeable to unlock new abilities, with features such as the <strong>propeller</strong> that allows Paran to glide from place to place and reach areas previously unexplorable.","developers":["Mattia Ciurlino"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1084830/header.jpg?t=1701997947","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256750208,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256750208/movie480.mp4?t=1557843676","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256750208/movie_max.mp4?t=1557843676"},"name":"MidKnight Story - Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256750208/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1557843676","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256750208/movie480.webm?t=1557843676","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256750208/movie_max.webm?t=1557843676"}}],"name":"MidKnight Story","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements